==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Enstamp
<hw>En*stamp"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To stamp; to mark
as with a stamp; to impress deeply.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>It is the motive . . . which <qex>enstamps</qex> the
character.</q> <rj><qau>Gogan.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Enstate</ent>⟦br⟧
